### lib/blog.ts Pattern (replicate for business)
- Reads markdown from content directory using `fs` + `gray-matter`
- In-memory cache class with 1hr TTL
- Supports `.md` and `.mdx` (prefers `.mdx`)
- `.md` compiled to HTML via `marked`, with `id` injected on `h2` tags
- `.mdx` raw source returned as string (compiled by `next-mdx-remote` in template)
- Exports: `getAllBlogPosts`, `getBlogPost(slug)`, `getAllBlogSlugs`

### blog/[slug]/page.tsx Pattern
- `export const revalidate = 86400`
- `generateStaticParams()` from slugs
- `generateMetadata()` ‚Äî full OG, Twitter, robots, canonical
- Template switcher via `post.template` frontmatter field
- 4 JSON-LD schemas injected via `generateSchemas()` from `src/lib/generateSchemas.ts`

